{"id":1012778817,"question_id":3,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"10 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1691231397,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"7 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1012778817/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"44.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        if(s.length()<2){\n            return s.length();\n        }\n        int i, j, index, max = 1;\n        HashMap<Character, Integer> found = new HashMap<>();\n        //int[] found = new int[26];\n        //Arrays.fill(found, -1);\n        for(i=0,j=0;i<s.length() && j<s.length();){\n            //index = s.charAt(j)-'a';\n            if(found.containsKey(s.charAt(j))){\n                int val = found.get(s.charAt(j));\n                max = Math.max(max, j-i);\n                while(i<=val){\n                    found.remove(s.charAt(i));\n                    i++;\n                }\n                continue;\n            }\n            found.put(s.charAt(j), j);\n            j++;\n        }\n        return max>(j-i)?max:j-i;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
